URL: https://github.com/maia-sh/ctregistries
BugReports: https://github.com/maia-sh/ctregistries/issues
Description: Regular expressions (regex) and R functions for trial registration numbers (TRN) from World Health Organization (WHO) International Clinical Trials Registry Platform (ICTRP) Primary Registries (https://www.who.int/ictrp/network/primary/en/) and MEDLINE Databank Sources (https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/medline_databank_source.html).
    Additional, non-trial databanks indexed by MEDLINE included without regexes.
